[recto] Adoration Brussels: For Bruegel as the author of the composition speaks: 1) Draping of the King; 2) the fact that used by Jan Brueghel in London etc. adoration [...]; 3) For Bruegel himself speaks this dog which he liked [...] 4) the triangular figure composition [...]; [verso] 5) The composition of the main group based 1564 (London) [...]; 6) The picture looks only at first sight very [...]; [kantlijn] Look up Kehrer: Drei Könige [= Hugo Kehrer, Die "Heiligen drei Könige" in der Legende und in der deutschen bildenden Kunst bis Albrecht Dürer, (Studien zur deutschen Kunstgeschichte; 53), Strassburg: Heitz, 1904 / Idem, Die Heiligen Drei Könige in Literatur und Kunst, Erster Band, Leipzig: Seemann,1908].[scan]
